            "title": "盤中速報 - 新晶投控(3713)大跌8.23%，報14.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新晶投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3713:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3713\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3713-TW</a>)24日13:15股價下跌1.3元，報14.5元，跌幅8.23%，成交205張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新晶投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3713:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3713\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3713-TW</a>)所屬產業為綠能環保，主要業務為一般投資業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌4.53%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲4.2%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+13 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+13 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
